Introduction

HIGH4 20 (Korean: 하이포투엔티; Japanese: 高4 20) is a duo under N.A.P. Entertainment. They were the first sub-unit of the boy group HIGH4. The sub-unit had two members, Alex and Youngjin.

They released their first single “HookGA” on October 3, 2016, which featured Hwasa from MAMAMOO.
